dialogueTree.title: Lilienne, the Net Picker: ""Huh... haven't seen the RCM around..."
dialogueTree.text: "Huh... haven't seen the RCM around for ages."

dialogueTree.title: Lilienne, the Net Picker: ""Thought you guys forgot this place..."
dialogueTree.text: "Thought you guys forgot this place even exists."

dialogueTree.title: Lilienne, the Net Picker: ""It's kinda nice seeing cops around..."
Lilienne, the Net Picker: ""Goddamnit... I *just* bought that..."
Lilienne, the Net Picker: ""I really need to get out there, ca..."
dialogueTree.text: "I really need to get out there, catch something."

dialogueTree.title: Lilienne, the Net Picker: ""Hey, kids! Oh... never mind.""
Lilienne, the Net Picker: ""The throw-nets just aren't paying..."
dialogueTree.text: "The throw-nets just aren't paying off this time of the year..."

dialogueTree.title: Lilienne, the Net Picker: ""It's yellowfin season soon.""
